Subject: [PATCH v3 04/17] clocksource/arm_arch_timer: Move system register timer programming over to CVAL
Date:   Sun, 10 Oct 2021 12:42:53 +0100
Message-Id: <20211010114306.2910453-5-maz@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.30.2
In-Reply-To: <20211010114306.2910453-1-maz@kernel.org>
